ign-center\"><em>As millennia passed, the war with Almarand continued above the cloud veil, until Zabava and her fellow Dragonslayers constructed a portal to the lands above. As the portal activated, Gaia awoke from her slumber, her connection to the realm reignited. With clairvoyance, she peered through the portal at the war above the clouds. Without her presence, the struggle for power had spiralled out of control. The time to strike had arrived.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Gaia left her sanctum and travelled to the scorched land beneath the cloud veil. There she befriended a lost and struggling Ragnar tribe, abandoned during the Cataclysm. Their pain and fury could be used to reclaim the realm. They spent days searching the barren landscape until finally, they reached the portal. Gaia turned to her followers before stepping through:<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>\u201cI am Gaia, Mother of the Realms. We will struggle, we will suffer, we will sacrifice. With our might we will wage a new war upon the lands above\u2026lay siege to our enemy\u2026claim what is rightfully ours. March forward, my friends &#8211; a better life awaits.\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Titanomachy begins, as <strong>GAIA<\/strong>, the All-Mother, enters the realm of the Shattered Kingdoms to assemble the Olympians and defeat the Titans!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"671\" height=\"572\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaSkills-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1038\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaSkills-3.png 671w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaSkills-3-300x256.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 671px) 100vw, 671px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Corrupted Goliaths <\/strong>have the following stat changes when compared to their regular counterparts:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>+150% Damage<\/li><li>+60% Health<\/li><li>Increased Size<\/li><li>Increased Speed<\/li><li>Elemental Resistances from Lvl 21-25<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Get her <em>terra-fic<\/em> <strong>signature Relics<\/strong> and more from the Milestone rewards:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"635\" height=\"435\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaRelics1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1028\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaRelics1.png 635w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaRelics1-300x206.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"635\" height=\"419\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaRelics2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1029\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaRelics2.png 635w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaRelics2-300x198.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Milestone Rewards<\/strong> are as follows:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"435\" height=\"1016\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaMilestones.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1030\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaMilestones.png 435w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/GaiaMilestones-128x300.png 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Alliance Leade